      <title>卢拉面临巨额预算赤字并吓跑投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/lula-is-running-huge-budget-deficits-and-scaring-off-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦重掌巴西政权已经快两年了。对于投资者来说，前景十分黯淡。巴西货币贬值，政府债券收益率上升，股市涨幅仅为其他新兴市场的一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/lula-is-running-huge-budget-deficits-and-scaring-off-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
